metadata.description: Meet Formacar Action NFT Collection that allows each early-bird player to access the magic world of P2E & D2E Racing! Using the Utility NFT Pass each holder will be able to login inside the Android and iOS Apps starting from the 18 December 2022. Players will get 233 $FCG tokens rewarded at the end of the Alpha Version testing period.
metadata.name: Alpha Version NFT Pass 1
